summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the City Light Department, granting an easement to Silver Lake Water District for a 16 inch water line across the City of Seattle's fee-owned Skagit Transmission Line Right-of-Way in the southeast quarter of Section 33, Township 28 North, Range 5 East, W.M., in Snohomish County, Washington (P.M. \#280533-4-301).
